---
title: Mumbai-Style Beef, Pork & Bacon Pie with Cheesy Mixed Mash Topping & Pear Salad
description: Potato topped pie is a weeknight dish we wait in anticipation for. Contain your excitement because this one has
cauliflower mashed into the topping and baked on richly spiced beef mince. We know you’ll love when the topping is
pulled apart and the Cheddar cheese stretches with it.
